name: Match Stick LED Ceiling Fixture
description: Matte black LED ceiling fixture with frosted white diffusers. Adjustable hanging cord (1.8m). Supports three color temperatures: 3000K, 4500K, 6000K. Remote included. Not dimmable.

name: Stick Pendant Frame Fixture
description: Matte black frame LED ceiling fixture with hanging stick pendants and chrome hardware. Adjustable cords (1.8m, 1.7m, 1.6m). Multi temperature LED: 3000K, 4500K, 6000K. Remote included. Not dimmable.

name: Modern Black Floor Lamp
description: Matte black LED floor lamp with slim body and round base. Warm white LED (3000K). Foot switch control. Minimalist modern design.

name: Vintage Wooden Table Lamp
description: Wooden table lamp with fabric shade. Warm ambient light using E26 bulb. Rustic vintage style. No remote control.

name: Chrome Glass Chandelier
description: Chrome chandelier with clear glass globes. Hanging chain installation. Elegant decorative lighting for dining rooms.

name: Industrial Wall Sconce
description: Matte black wall sconce with exposed Edison bulb design. Adjustable arm for directing light. Suitable for indoor use in living rooms or hallways.

name: Brass Desk Lamp
description: Brass finish desk lamp with adjustable arm and head. Uses E26 bulb for focused task lighting. Classic design for office or study.

name: Contemporary LED Ceiling Light
description: Sleek white LED ceiling light with diffuser. Flush mount design. Cool white light (6000K). Energy-efficient and long-lasting.

name: Rustic Lantern Pendant
description: Rustic metal lantern pendant light with glass panels. Hanging chain installation. Warm white light for cozy ambiance.

name: Minimalist LED Wall Light
description: Slim LED wall light with matte black finish. Provides soft ambient lighting. Easy installation and energy-efficient design.

name: Art Deco Table Lamp
description: Art Deco style table lamp with geometric patterns and gold accents. Uses E26 bulb for warm light. Stylish addition to living rooms or bedrooms.

name: Scandinavian Floor Lamp
description: Scandinavian design floor lamp with wooden tripod base and fabric shade. Warm white LED (3000K). Foot switch control for easy operation.

name: Mid-Century Modern Chandelier
description: Mid-century modern chandelier with brass finish and globe shades. Hanging chain installation. Elegant lighting for dining or living areas.
